617718 9 Repeal and saving.-
853278 1The Taxation Laws (Amendment) Ordinance, 2001 (Ord. 2 of 2001) is hereby repealed.
1061528 2Notwithstanding such repeal, anything done or any action taken under the said Ordinance shall be deemed to have been done or taken under the corresponding provisions of this Act. SUBHASH C. JAIN, Secy. to the Govt. of India.
CORRIGENDUM
In the Coal India (Regulation of Transfers and Validation) Act, 2000 (45 of 2000) as published in the Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 1, dated the 8th December, 2000 (Issue No. 59), at page 2, in line 26, for" land of rights", read" land or rights".
